content:
[[include :scp-wiki:theme:black-highlighter-theme]]
[[module CSS]]
h1, h2 {
    text-align: center;
}

.step_container {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    border: 1px solid #999;
    padding: 1em;
}

#page-title {
    display: none;
}

#page-content > .collapsible-block {
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0.75em;
    background-color: lightgrey;
    border-top: 0.125rem dashed slategrey;
    border-bottom: 0.125rem dashed slategrey;
}

#page-content > div.collapsible-block > div.collapsible-block-unfolded > div.collapsible-block-content {
    text-align:left;
}
[[/module]]
+ Anomaly Classification Bar Lite
----
[[>]]
[[module rate]]
[[/>]]
[[div class="step_container"]]
+ [/anomaly-classification-system-guide BEFORE USING, PLEASE READ THIS GUIDE].
++ Please read [[[component:anomaly-class-bar|Anomaly Classification Bar]]] for further information.
----
[[=]]
+++ Black Highlighter is not required to use this component.
+++ This component can co-exist with the original ACS component.
[[/=]]
[[/div]]

[[div class="step_container"]]
[[=]]
++++ This is a derivative version of the ACS that unifies line thickness ({{3px}}) and takes up less space on most devices (almost 1/2 the size of the original ACS on mobile devices).

++++ This component is not compatible with existing ACS addons.
[[/=]]
[[/div]]

+ EXAMPLE

[[include component:acs-horm-lite-source
|item-number= 2105
|clearance= 2
|container-class= euclid
|secondary-class= none
|disruption-class= vlam
|risk-class= notice
]]
@@ @@
[[include component:acs-horm-lite-source
|item-number= 3000
|clearance= 5
|container-class= esoteric
|secondary-class= thaumiel
|secondary-icon= http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Aanomaly-class-bar/thaumiel-icon.svg
|disruption-class= ekhi
|risk-class= critical
]]
@@ @@
[[include component:acs-horm-lite-source
|item-number= 4511
|clearance= 4
|container-class= pending
|secondary-class= none
|disruption-class= none
|risk-class= none
]]

------

