+ HOW TO USE
[[div class="step_container"]]
[[=]]
++++ Include this component in the same way as the original ACS component, just change

++++ [[span style="background-color: rgba(var(--five-color), 0.15); color: rgb(var(--five-color))"]]{{anomaly-class-bar-source}}[[/span]]

++++ to

++++ [[span style="background-color: rgba(var(--one-color), 0.15); color: rgb(var(--one-color))"]]{{acs-horm-lite-source}}[[/span]]
[[/=]]
[[/div]]

+ EXTRA OPTIONS

[[include component:acs-horm-lite-source
